{"tid":2045952,"cid":22,"subCid":0,"title":"求教學用實物投影機推薦","createTime":"2020-06-01T06:12:40.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-01T09:51:31.000Z","uid":137674,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"9f9624e80fbb7f9469ab0906e30fc9f9472034f5","tid":2045952,"uid":137674,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-01T06:12:40.000Z","msg":"畫質1080p以上, 用途如下：<br />\n1. 可以駁電腦錄教學片<br />\n2. 可以駁電腦當鏡頭咁做Zoom直播教學<br />\n3. 可以駁電視做projector screen<br />\n<br />\n已經google過香港好少呢d資料, <a href=\"http://price.com.hk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fprice.com.hk&d=jFWDEiyvEellqADaqpERGkkSG0DzaVerHR9pE4rwCb4%3D&h=a5472559\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">price.com.hk</a>得幾個model<br />\n<br />\n仲有而家好多投影機主要用途係掃描文件/invoice, 但scan野對我黎講係其次, 最重要是教個陣夠清無拖延/拖影, 可以自動對焦等。可以掃描ocr數學公式符號至file最好, 但唔係必須。<br />\n<br />\n投影機示意圖<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.highprosper.com.hk/images/visualizer.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.highprosper.com.hk%2Fimages%2Fvisualizer.jpg&h=e6b79864&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n求推薦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8cc22e104eb83cd2300d8c22313082f850dc5808","tid":2045952,"uid":60860,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-01T06:44:32.000Z","msg":"好耐無見過<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />依家中學仲有無"},{"pid":"551fe02bca044eb64743fe4361c48bf30e746e41","tid":2045952,"uid":52068,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8cc22e104eb83cd2300d8c22313082f850dc5808","tid":2045952,"uid":60860,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-01T06:44:32.000Z","msg":"好耐無見過<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />依家中學仲有無"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-01T09:03:33.000Z","msg":"換曬類似web cam嗰啲，細細舊"},{"pid":"14580eaf1de44feab7461a3259d5bb9138dce7b4","tid":2045952,"uid":256094,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-01T09:08:26.000Z","msg":"諗返起以前d黃燈個d幻燈片<i